ngle chart|Billboardrandbhiphop|9|artist=XXXTentacion|rowheader=true|accessdate=July 3, 2018}}\n|-\n{{single chart|Billboardrhythmic|20|artist=XXXTentacion|rowheader=true|accessdate=November 20, 2018}}\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Year-end charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2018)\n! scope=\"col\"| Position\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Canada (Canadian Hot 100)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2018/canadian-hot-100|title=Canadian Hot 100 \u2013 Year-End 2018|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 4, 2018}}</ref>\n| 71\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Denmark (Tracklisten)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://hitlisten.nu/2018_track_t100.html|title=Track Top-100 2018|publisher=Hitlisten|language=Danish|accessdate=January 16, 2019}}</ref>\n| 66\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| New Zealand (Recorded Music NZ)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4568|title=Top Selling Singles of 2018|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|accessdate=December 13, 2018}}</ref>\n| 49\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Sweden (Sverigetopplistan)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/lista?liid=43&dfom=20180001|title=\u00c5rslista Singlar \u2013 \u00c5r 2018|publisher=Sverigetopplistan|language=Swedish|accessdate=January 15, 2019}}</ref>\n| 88\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Switzerland (Schweizer Hitparade)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://hitparade.ch/charts/jahreshitparade/2018|title=Schweizer Jahreshitparade 2018 \u2013 hitparade.ch|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=December 31, 2018}}</ref>\n| 58\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US ''Billboard'' Hot 100<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2018/hot-100-songs|title=Hot 100 Songs \u2013 Year-End 2018|work=Billboard|accessdate=December 4, 2018}}</ref>\n| 88\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| US Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs (''Billboard'')<ref>{{cite web|title=Hot R&B/Hip-Hop Songs \u2013 Year-End 2018|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2018/hot-r-and-and-b-hip-hop-so